Title: Unisex retro Casio green resin strap watch F-91WC-3AEF
Description: chapelle_jewellery Visit our eBay Shop Add us to your Favourites list > Subscribe to our Newsletter > About Chapelle Delivery The Chapelle Guarantee Unisex retro Casio green resin strap watch F-91WC-3AEF RRP £22.00 Now £14.00 Description This fantastic luminous green timepiece from Casio is the perfect watch for every occasion and adds a bold colour to your outfits. The comfortable yet secured fitting of the green resin strap that has been given a simple buckle clasp to ensure that the watch is fastened securely to the wrist. Surrounding the LCD dial is a green plastic casing with white detailing showing you what each of the silver toned buttons do. The digital display shows the time in 12/24 hour format depending on the option you choose. This Casio classic has a limited amount of features which include a stopwatch, an alarm to remind you of everyday or any recurring events, a backlight illuminator and a date and calendar display. This illuminator is splash proof however should not be immersed in water. All Casio watches come supplied in official Casio presentation boxes inside the box there is a 2 year manufacturers reference.
